Flag install_tests
  Description: Install test library (for developers)
  Default: false

Flag all
  Description: build and install everything
  Default: false

Library covar
  Pack:               false
  Build:              true
  Path:               src/lib
  Modules:            Covar_optional_args, Covar_float, Covar_gamma, Covar_bessel, Covar_trig,
                      Covar_instance, Covar_kernel, Covar_predictive, Covar_loss, Covar
  BuildDepends:       threads, core, containers, containers.data, lacaml, gsl, ppx_deriving,
                      ppx_deriving.make, ppx_deriving.show
  XMETADescription:   Covariance functions for machine learning.

Library kernels
   Path:              src/lib/kernels
