                      Covar_linear, Covar_periodic
   FindLibParent:     covar
   Build:             true
   BuildDepends:      covar, lacaml, gsl

Library test
  Path: src/test
  Build$: flag(tests) || flag(all)
  FindLibParent: covar
  Modules: Covar_test
  Install$: flag(install_tests)
  BuildDepends: kaputt, covar

Executable test_kernel
  Path:               src/test
  Build$:             flag(tests) || flag(all)
  MainIs:             test_kernel.ml
  BuildDepends:       kaputt, covar.kernels, covar.test

Test test_kernel
  Command: $test_kernel
  TestTools: test_kernel
  Run$: flag(tests) || flag(all)

